*************
Program 8 Use
*************

Compilation: \i p8.sql

Usage Example: select program8('T5', 'V2', 'A3', 119.99); 	EX. For transaction whose transaction number is "T5", vendor number is "V2', customer account number is "A3", with an amount of $119.99


